data.description: Awesome, peaceful, private property with beautiful mountain & valley views! Almost 12 acres of space with plenty of room for all your toys & animals! Kitchen offers upgraded granite countertops, maple cabinets & stainless appliances. Custom windows throughout! Living Room with new French Doors, Family Room with New Glass Storm Door & Ring Doorbell/Camera. One bedroom converted to a computer room which can easily be restored back, closet doors in storage. Newly Painted interior, New LED light fixtures, Cellular Blinds & Evap Cooler. Low Maintenance Yard. Exterior with Graveled driveway, Decorative rock in front & side of house. New patio area, retaining wall & pavers with sail shades. 12x24 Toy Shed with rollup doors & side entry. Home is equipped with Starlink Satellite Service which provides Fast Internet & phone service, sellers will be leaving the equipment for new buyers.  VA eligible buyer may be able to assume loan at 2.75% interest rate. Washer & Dryer,  85" TV (1 yr old) Center Channel with High End Surround Speaker System negotiable with the right offer.   Come see this Awesome home, a retreat from the hustle & bustle of life!!
